  "title": "Sales Consultant",
  "description": "<p>🌟<strong> Join Singapore’s Leading Maid Agency – Island Maids </strong>🌟<br /></p><p><strong>Build a Rewarding Career with a Trusted Brand</strong></p><p>Island Maids is Singapore’s <strong>largest and most reputable maid agency</strong>, dedicated to connecting families with reliable domestic helpers. With <strong>11 conveniently located branches</strong> across the island, we’re proud to serve thousands of happy clients.<br /></p><ol><li>Bedok</li><li>Yishun</li><li>Jurong</li><li>Hougang</li><li>Ang Mo Kio</li><li>Tiong Bahru</li><li>Bukit Timah</li><li>Race Course</li><li>Marine Parade</li><li>Punggol</li><li>Tampines</li></ol><p>At Island Maids, we <strong>believe in people</strong> — our clients, our helpers, and most importantly, our team. We’re more than colleagues; we’re a <strong>close-knit team</strong> working together to deliver exceptional service and support every step of the hiring journey.<br /></p><p>💼<strong> Why You’ll Love Working With Us</strong></p><ul><li>🗓️ <strong>5-day work week</strong> (flexible schedule for better work-life balance)</li><li>💰 <strong>Attractive starting salary</strong> – commensurate with experience</li><li>💎 <strong>High commissions & performance incentives</strong></li><li>📝 <strong>Leads Distribution & Support </strong>given to achieve your targets</li><li>🌍 <strong>Annual overseas incentive trips</strong> - work hard, play harder.</li><li>🤝 <strong>Supportive team culture</strong> – we grow and win together</li><li></li></ul><p>🚀<strong> Who We’re Looking For</strong></p><p>If you’re <strong>driven, people-oriented, and passionate about sales</strong>, this is the perfect opportunity to build a fulfilling career in a fast-growing industry.</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>CEI certification (advantage)</li><li>Experience in the employment or service industry preferred</li><li>Self-motivated, target-driven, and customer-focused</li><li>Confident in conducting and arranging client interviews</li><li>Able to manage day-to-day branch operations</li><li>A positive attitude and a strong team spirit</li></ul><p>🌐<strong> Be Part of Our Story</strong></p><p>Join a brand that values growth, teamwork, and excellence.<br />📍 Learn more about us at <a href=\"http://www.islandmaids.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.islandmaids.com.sg</a><br /><br />💬 We can’t wait to hear from you — your next big opportunity starts here!</p>",
